#### **Challenges and Criticisms**

| **Issue** | **Details** |
|---------|-----------|
| **Non-Binding** | No enforcement mechanism; relies on state goodwill. |
| **FPIC Ambiguity** | "Consent" vs. "consultation" debated (e.g., Canada’s TMX pipeline). |
| **Corporate Pushback** | Mining/oil industries lobby against land rights. |
| **Digital Gaps** | UNDRIP silent on AI, data sovereignty—**FPT fills this via glyphs**. |

